<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>ʿạdl ḥbyb, ʿạdl ḥbyb</author>
<hymn_number>10337</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr - klmẗ yqwlhạlk qlby qbl mạ ạqwlhạ blsạny ḥbyby yạ yswʿ

[V2]
 lạnk ạnt ḥbytny ḥb bkl ạlmʿạny ḥbyby yạ yswʿ

[V3]
 1- ḥsyt bḥbk lyạ ḥty wạnạ fy ạlkẖṭyẗ

[V4]
 knt kẖạyf ʿlyạ ḥbyby yạ yswʿ

[V5]
 2- ạnt ạlly rḍyt tqblny bʿd ạlʿạlm mạ krhny

[V6]
 ywm mạ trdny ạstnytny ḥbyby yạ yswʿ

[V7]
 3- ạnt ạlly ạtḥnnt ʿlyạ wạnạ ʿạysẖ fy ạlʿbwdyẗ

[V8]
 wlqytk frḥạn byạ ḥbyby yạ yswʿ

[V9]
 4- wsẖrbt ạlkạs mkạny ḥmlt ʿạry wạḥzạny

[V10]
 wrḍyt tmwt ʿlsẖạny ḥbyby yạ yswʿ</lyrics>
<title>ḥbyby yạ yswʿ</title>
</song>